
# 100 Flutter Challenge - Coin Tracker

This Flutter project is part of the 100 Flutter Challenge series and aims to create a coin tracking application. The app allows users to search and keep track of the rates of various cryptocurrencies in Indian Rupees (INR), along with the increase or decrease in their prices.

## Features

- Fetches data from CoinGecko API to get real-time market data for cryptocurrencies.
- Displays a list of the top 100 cryptocurrencies based on market capitalization.
- Allows users to search for specific cryptocurrencies by name or symbol.
- Shows the current price of each cryptocurrency in INR.
- Indicates the percentage change in price over the last 24 hours.
- Provides a detailed view of a selected cryptocurrency, including additional information such as market cap, volume, and price chart.
- Supports smooth scrolling and navigation within the app.
- Utilizes clean and responsive UI design to enhance user experience.

